    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:1.2",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena paccanīkasāto nāma brāhmaṇo sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati. ",
          "en": "Now at that time a brahmin named Contraphile, who loved contradiction, was residing in Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho paccanīkasātassa brāhmaṇassa etadahosi: ",
          "en": "Then Contraphile thought, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:1.4",
          "pli": "“yannūnāhaṃ yena samaṇo gotamo tenupasaṅkameyyaṃ. ",
          "en": "“Why don’t I go to the ascetic Gotama and "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:1.5",
          "pli": "Yaṃ yadeva samaṇo gotamo bhāsissati taṃ tadevassāhaṃ paccanīkāssan”ti. ",
          "en": "contradict everything he says?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:1.6",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā abbhokāse caṅkamati. ",
          "en": "At that time the Buddha was walking meditation in the open air. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:1.7",
          "pli": "Atha kho paccanīkasāto brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ caṅkamantaṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "Then the brahmin Contraphile went up to the Buddha, and said to him as he was walking meditation, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:1.8",
          "pli": "“bhaṇa samaṇadhamman”ti. ",
          "en": "“Ascetic, preach the Dhamma.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:2.1",
          "pli": "“Na paccanīkasātena, ",
          "en": "“Fine words aren’t easy to understand "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:2.2",
          "pli": "suvijānaṃ subhāsitaṃ; ",
          "en": "by a lover of contradiction, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:2.3",
          "pli": "Upakkiliṭṭhacittena, ",
          "en": "whose mind is tainted "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:2.4",
          "pli": "sārambhabahulena ca. ",
          "en": "and full of aggression. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:3.1",
          "pli": "Yo ca vineyya sārambhaṃ, ",
          "en": "But when you’ve dispelled aggression, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:3.2",
          "pli": "appasādañca cetaso; ",
          "en": "and your suspicious mind, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:3.3",
          "pli": "Āghātaṃ paṭinissajja, ",
          "en": "and you’ve got rid of resentment, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:3.4",
          "pli": "sa ve jaññā subhāsitan”ti. ",
          "en": "then you’ll understand fine words.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:4.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ vutte, paccanīkasāto brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "When he had spoken, the brahmin Contraphile said to the Buddha, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:4.2",
          "pli": "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … ",
          "en": "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn7.16:4.3",
          "pli": "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. ",
          "en": "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.”"
        }
      ],
